{"type": "article", "id": 28093, "title": "3D 打印灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-13T07:00:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152610sMIwch4kF75DAJPV.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>纽约设计师 Christo Logan 最近将古老的陶瓷工艺和数码建模技术结合在一起，推出 3D 打印灯系列 two.parts。每一款灯具都采用中空的结构，把 LED 灯、电线等配件隐藏了起来。光线从灯罩内侧发出，配合优雅的流线型外观呈现出一种奇妙的光照效果。two.parts 系列共有 12 种不同的模型，有七种不同的颜色可选，这是它的<a href=\"http://two.parts/store/\">购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021526086Kudj8VyQGxHsBM0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152608VGn5QA0CNpW24q36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152609Mv6knH9diwITJGzV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152610t4U3yAEI6YnZDXTc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}